Thatâ€™s a Twitter::Error::Unauthorized exception.
You may have noticed we are taking a different direction with our own design: although these situations are exceptional for the gem, they are not exceptional for our wrapper class; they are just part of the normal workflow. That said, we can visualize our wrapper as an adapter which happens to â€œfixâ€ these mistakes and massage the data to a format our application can easily consume.
